text: Saint Joseph Central Catholic High School is a private, Catholic high school in Ironton, Ohio. It is operated by the Roman Catholic Diocese of Steubenville. The school's sports teams are known as the Flyers. In addition to housing the high school grades of 9-12, the school also houses junior high grades 7–8. ==References== ==External links== * Category:High schools in Lawrence County, Ohio Category:Catholic secondary schools in Ohio Category:Ironton, Ohio Category:Private middle schools in Ohio
